uHlelo lokusebenza elibala incedezelo yokuxhumana.

Ngabe izindawo zama-Webu nama amakhasi okuxhumana evalewe yeni na?

Ingabe ukuxhuma kwe-internet kusebenza kancane kunoku jwayelekele? Sebenziza u-OONI Probe ukwazi!
Imininigwane yakho eku-OONI Probe ishicilelwe kanye nemininingwane yakho yenethiwekhi.
Noma ubana ogade ukusebenzisa kwakho kwe-Internet (umzekelo. uhulumeni noma ISP) uyabona ukuthi usebenzisa i-OONI Probe .
Kungenzeka uhlole ama-Website angavumelikile (kodwa uyakwazi ukukhetha amakhasi ofuna ukuwahlola).
Uma kukhona umuntu ogade umsebenzi we-intanethi yami, uzobona ukuthi ngisebenzisa i-OONI Probe.
i-OONI Probe akulona ithuluzi lemfihlo. Noma ubani ogade umsebenzi we-intanethi yakho uzobona ukuthi iyiphi i-sofware oyisebenzisayo.
Ngaso sonke iskhathi ngisebenzisa i-OONI Probe, imininingwane ye-intanethi engiyiqoqayo izoshicilikeka ngokuzenzakalelayo.
Ukukhuphula ukungafihli kwengcindezelo ye-intanethi, umsebenzi wenethiwekhi yabo bonke abasebenzisi ba-OONI Probe iyashicileka ngokuzenzakalelayo (ngaphandle uma bephuma kwama-settings).
Ukuthuthukisa i-Ooni Probe singathanda ukuqoqoqa ukusaphazeka kwemibiko engaziwa uma i-App ingasebenzi kahle\n\nUngathanda ukuthumela imibiko yokusaphazeka eqembini lika Ooni?
